I couldn’t believe what had just happened, what had just been done, not even what he said.
He asked me if he could kiss me. And he did it with a face that was so… cute.
His eyes had a special sparkle that I won’t be able to forget.

Considering how many guys wouldn’t ask and would just go ahead without caring about your true feelings, he asked for permission. He wanted to know if I was willing.
And that was without even reading any of the letter…
So, does he have any ideas?, will he even expect anything from what he’s about to read?

Whatever it was, he listened to what I told him.

Before the letter, I attached a note clearly specifying that he shouldn’t say anything until we saw each other and were alone, just the two of us.

do set_background("negroo")
Two days passed, which felt like an eternity, after that.

Just yesterday, right after finishing the exam, Mateo asked me if we could meet on the 16th. Without thinking, I said yes. And at what a cost.

I should have said no and postponed the meeting until I was truly ready, but if I’m being honest, had I delayed that meeting to another day or until I felt prepared, I would never have seen him.
That meeting would never have happened, because I would always feel these nerves coursing through my body.
I would never have been truly ready to see him in person, to talk to him face to face.
Simply put, that moment I thought would be perfect for when I was ready to talk to him would never really come.

And, without realizing how quickly that span of time passed, which I had thought would be longer, the moment arrived.

do set_background("habitacionMasOscura")
